OL,6,FA gold pocket watch that was recovered
OL,7,Ffrom the body of the richest man on
OL,8,Fthe Titanic has sold for a record-
OL,9,Fbreaking #1.175 million.
OL,11,FThe watch was sold on Saturday to a
OL,12,Fprivate collector in the US at Henry
OL,13,FAldridge & Son in Devizes, Wiltshire,
OL,14,Ffor the highest amount ever for
OL,15,FTitanic memorabilia, the auctioneers
OL,16,Fsaid.
