OL,6,FThe original owner of the watch,
OL,7,Fbusinessman John Jacob Astor, 47, went
OL,8,Fdown with the ship in 1912 after
OL,9,Fseeing new wife Madeleine onto a
OL,10,Flifeboat.
OL,12,FThe previous highest amount paid for
OL,13,FTitanic artefacts was #1.1 million for
OL,14,Fa violin that was played as the ship
OL,15,Fsank ` which sold at the same auction
OL,16,Fhouse in 2013, according to the
OL,17,Fauctioneers.
