OL,6,F"112 years later, we are still talking
OL,7,Fabout the ship and the passengers and
OL,8,Fthe crew.
OL,10,F"The thing with the Titanic story,
OL,11,Fit's effectively a large ship hits an
OL,12,Ficeberg with a tragic loss of life,
OL,13,Fbut more importantly is 2,200 stories.
OL,15,F"2,200 subplots, every man woman and
OL,16,Fchild had a story to tell and then the
OL,17,Fmemorabilia tells those stories today."
