OL,6,FMr Aldridge said: "Astor is well known
OL,7,Fas the richest passenger aboard the
OL,8,FRMS Titanic and was thought to be
OL,9,Famong the richest people in the world
OL,10,Fat that time, with a net worth of
OL,11,Froughly 87 million US dollars `
OL,12,Fequivalent to several billion dollars
OL,13,Ftoday.
OL,15,F"At 11.40pm on April 14 1912, the
OL,16,FTitanic hit an iceberg and started to
OL,17,Ftake on water.
